  "title": "Pilates Reformer Instructor (Freelance)",
  "description": "<p>Conduct Pilates Reformer classes for individuals and groups.</p>\n<p>Provide personalized guidance and support to clients, ensuring a safe and effective workout.</p>\n<p>Develop and modify workout routines based on individual needs and fitness levels.</p>\n<p>Maintain a positive and encouraging atmosphere in the studio.</p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Certification in Pilates Reformer instruction.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n<p>Hourly rate of $30 to $40 per class depending on experience.</p>",
